    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused BMW E46 M3, a quintessential example of Bavarian engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry perform as intended. While showing signs of honest use consistent with its enthusiast pedigree, the mechanical vitals remain robust, delivering the visceral, linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback that defined an era of performance motoring.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
